SUMMARY:Pollinator Party!
DESCRIPTION:Let’s have a party for our pollinators who are back to work this spring. Participate in pollinator-themed crafts and games and learn to do the waggle dance. Take a guided walk through our native plant garden to see what’s in bloom and who is buzzing around. Enjoy a cup of herbal tea or apple juice and a honey lollipop\, all courtesy of our pollinator friends. This is an open house style event-come any time between 3-5pm and stay for as long as you’d like! \nCOST: This is a FREE event\, but we highly encourage a donation to support the Nature Center of Cape May. \nWHEN: Tuesday\, April 14th\, 3pm-5pm \nWHERE: Nature Center of Cape May (1600 Delaware Avenue\, Cape May\, NJ\, 08204)
URL:https://njaudubon.org/event/pollinator-party/
LOCATION:Nature Center of Cape May\, 1600 Delaware Avenue\, Cape May\, NJ\, 08204\, United States
